snippet.title: Puffmin Quest - Trailer 3 | Pikmin 2 Mod
snippet.description:
The third trailer for JaySalty's Pikmin 2 mod Puffmin Quest that was originally submitted to @TongPik3 's Fan-Made Pikmin Direct.

This trailer features a bunch of new additions to the project!
